{{> admin/seatmap/layout/header}}

<link href="/css/admin/seatmap-workspace.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="/css/admin/seatmap-concert-stage3.css" rel="stylesheet">

<body>
<div class="app" id="stage3App" data-stage4-url="/admin/seatmap/concert/stage4">
    <div class="seatmap-workspace seatmap-workspace--stage3">

        {{> admin/seatmap/layout/workspace-concert-stage3}}

        <main class="seatmap-main stage3-main">
            <div class="seatmap-command-bar" aria-label="작업 명령">
                <button type="button" class="seatmap-command-btn" id="zoomOut">－ 축소</button>
                <button type="button" class="seatmap-command-btn" id="zoomReset">100%</button>
                <button type="button" class="seatmap-command-btn" id="zoomIn">＋ 확대</button>
                <span class="seatmap-zoom-value" id="zoomValue">100%</span>
            </div>

            <div class="stage3-board">
                <section class="stage3-map-card" id="mapCard">
                    <div class="stage3-card-head">
                        <strong>배치도 미니맵</strong>
                        <span>구역 클릭 → 아래 좌석 편집 화면에 표시</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stage3-mini-frame" id="miniFrame">
                        <canvas id="miniCanvas"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stage3-map-help">
                        휠로 확대/축소, 드래그로 이동합니다. 숫자 라벨 없이 구역 형태만 표시합니다.
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="stage3-editor-card" id="editorCard">
                    <div class="stage3-card-head stage3-card-head--editor">
                        <strong id="canvasTitle">파트1 · 기준 구역 선택</strong>
                        <span id="sizeText">-</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="stage3-seat-editor" id="seatCanvasBox">
                        <canvas id="seatBase"></canvas>
                        <canvas id="seatOverlay"></canvas>

                        <div class="seat-action-popover" id="seatActionPopover" aria-hidden="true">
                            <button type="button" id="applyRemove">삭제</button>
                            <button type="button" id="applyAvailable">복구</button>
                            <button type="button" id="applyObstructed">장애석</button>
                            <button type="button" id="clearSelection">해제</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>

        <aside class="seatmap-side seatmap-side--right stage3-right">
            <div class="box stage3-info-box">
                <h3>선택 구역</h3>
                <div class="stats stage3-stat-grid">
                    <div class="stat"><b id="selName">-</b><span>구역</span></div>
                    <div class="stat"><b id="selCount">0</b><span>좌석</span></div>
                    <div class="stat"><b id="selectedCount">0</b><span>선택</span></div>
                    <div class="stat"><b id="selObstructed">0</b><span>장애석</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="box stage3-tool-box">
                <h3>좌석 크기 / 간격 확정</h3>
                <p class="help-text">Part2에서 선택 구역의 실제 좌석 크기와 간격을 확정합니다.</p>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="seatWidthRange">좌석 너비 <b id="seatWidthValue">18px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="seatWidthRange" min="6" max="48" value="18">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="seatHeightRange">좌석 높이 <b id="seatHeightValue">18px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="seatHeightRange" min="6" max="48" value="18">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="gapXRange">가로 간격 <b id="gapXValue">4px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="gapXRange" min="0" max="36" value="4">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="gapYRange">세로 간격 <b id="gapYValue">4px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="gapYRange" min="0" max="36" value="4">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="paddingXRange">가로 여백 <b id="paddingXValue">14px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="paddingXRange" min="0" max="80" value="14">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="paddingYRange">세로 여백 <b id="paddingYValue">14px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="paddingYRange" min="0" max="80" value="14">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="offsetXRange">전체 X 이동 <b id="offsetXValue">0px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="offsetXRange" min="-160" max="160" value="0">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-range-field">
                    <label for="offsetYRange">전체 Y 이동 <b id="offsetYValue">0px</b></label>
                    <input type="range" id="offsetYRange" min="-160" max="160" value="0">
                </div>

                <div class="stage3-tool-actions">
                    <button type="button" class="btn" id="resetLayoutBtn">배치값 초기화</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn--green" id="saveLayoutBtn">작업 저장</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="box stage3-help-box">
                <h3>작업 기준</h3>
                <div class="help-text">
                    Part1에서 기준 구역과 좌석 수를 잡고 전체 구역을 자동 추정합니다.
                    Part2에서 좌석 크기, 간격, 위치를 확정하고 좌석을 선택해 삭제/복구/장애석 처리합니다.
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script src="/js/admin/seatmap-workspace.js" defer></script>
<script src="/js/admin/seatmap-concert-stage3.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
